{"tid":102320,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"20歲美女年初4   玩過山車死亡","createTime":"2017-01-31T14:10:12.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-31T15:54:53.000Z","uid":58099,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6f789bf83e948e74776c828f15d172b6362dbe82","tid":102320,"uid":58099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T14:10:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/01/31/220825_89dbf202b48fbd200b48847672217b3c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F01%2F31%2F220825_89dbf202b48fbd200b48847672217b3c.jpg&h=529b4cbd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n       1月31日，一名浙江台州籍遊客在寧波方特東方神話主題樂園中的「叢林飛龍」(木制過山車)項目排隊區等待時，突然暈倒，送院搶救無效死亡。<br />\n<br />\n      寧波方特東方神話主題樂園工作人員稱，上午10點半左右，在叢林飛龍項目排隊等候區，有一名20歲的女性遊客突然暈倒地上，公園人員馬上送遊客至醫院救治。經醫院證實，年輕女遊客入院時已無生命體徵，搶救無效死亡。<br />\n<br />\n　　寧波方特東方神畫，位於寧波杭州灣新區跨海大橋南岸。而園區內的「叢林飛龍」是中國東部最大的木質過山車。"},{"pid":"d79d91cc2620950f780f4e8d7803c3e6994e76bf","tid":102320,"uid":294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T14:11:59.000Z","msg":"😭"},{"pid":"3b5f9a7c00c0754ab9ea8b1cec7205a5f5e93347","tid":102320,"uid":18569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T14:14:07.000Z","msg":"Rip<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cbda071a96ed33f15bae5e99a1cd0e3cb3eb2971","tid":102320,"uid":19837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T14:15:45.000Z","msg":"又死一件"},{"pid":"ee72cf8d410f63db4c44e96c596fff9c2119e790","tid":102320,"uid":41818,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T14:16:05.000Z","msg":"想屌 唔好曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff1d17677184cd6dc6b9aca193751040139848a3","tid":102320,"uid":4826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T14:16:28.000Z","msg":"標題黨"},{"pid":"b48f40733156c3168f7a1337dea8033ff5261624","tid":102320,"uid":9736,"like":0,"dislike